# **Goughless Kalameet**

**Goughless Kalameet** is a sequence break that allows the player to defeat [**Black Dragon Kalameet**](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/black-dragon-kalameet) without having [Hawkeye Gough](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/hawkeye-gough) shoot him down with his greatbow.

Normally, Kalameet flies constantly, making him nearly impossible to hit. By using specific positioning, players can kill the dragon while he is still airborne.

If you want to learn even more about this strategy and the history behind it , here is a video [https://youtu.be/lzr3QZFAq9k](https://youtu.be/lzr3QZFAq9k) by catalystz on YouTube.

